                  </hi>(<hi rend="italic">police-constable A</hi>36.) I took the prisoner—he said he did do it, and that when one of the ladies screamed he dropped it—he had another handkerchief in his trowsers' pocket, which he could give no account of—he said it belonged to his brother.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was going after a situation—I was running, and saw two ladies after you—then you took me—the only words I said to the policeman were, "Don't drag me in that manner, allow me to speak to the gentleman"—this is my brother's handkerchief.</p>
